4. the japanese is between the british and the pakistani##2
5. the person driving the skateboard is the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the boat and the pakistani##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
