.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, video-games, gardening, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, musical, adventure, action
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | gardening | sudoku | video-games   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | adventure | animation      | action |

