.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, guinea-pig, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, cycling, climbing, cricket
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | goldfish | turtle   | guinea-pig      | rat      |
| Sport   | cycling     | climbing | sailing | cricket |

