.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, r&b, pop, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, polish, american, indonesian
1. the thai is on the right of the polish##1
2. the fan of pop is between the indonesian and the polish##2
3. the fan of r&b is the polish##1
4. the american is on the left of the polish##1
5. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the thai##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | funk | r&b | pop      | trance   |
| Nationality   | american  | polish    | thai | indonesian |

