.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, rock-climbing, gardening
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, roller
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
5. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | drawing | rock-climbing | gardening    | fishing      |
| Transport   | motorbike       | roller       | helicopter | bike |

