2. the thai is the thai##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the mexican##3
5. the french is on the left or right of the spanish##3
6. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the spanish##3
7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

