2. the dressmaker is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the dressmaker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating avocado is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
