.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, gardening, fishing, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, electronic, soul, ambient
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the fan of ambient##1
4. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
6. the fan of soul is the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | woodworking | fishing | chess |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | gospel       | electronic   | soul      |

