3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
4. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of trance##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Beverage      | mirinda | coffee    | iced-tea  | water |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | soul | reggae | ambient  |

