.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, iced-tea, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, volleyball, biathlon, soccer
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee     | tea     | iced-tea          | juice |
| Sport      | parkour | volleyball | soccer | biathlon  |

 